race.comment: ROSES RING (2) looks close to another win after finishing third from Box 1 last time (20.83) at Nowra. Boasts a strong record from this draw with three wins and two minor placings from six starts. Makes plenty of appeal. ARIA'S DREAM (7) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (20.76) at Nowra. Expected to be in this for a long way. TRIUMPH (1) was unwanted in betting when starting from the same box but ran very well, finishing in the minors over 350m at this track in a Mix 2/3 in 20.32. Good beginner and aided by the inside draw. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. SPRING GOLD (8) should be thereabouts.
